data.description: IGNORE DOM, same buyer fell out twice each time days before closing!!!  Fabulous single level home backing green space!!  No neighbors behind!!!   Well maintained, freshly painted, newer AC includes warranty and new turf in the private backyard!! The perfect Open, split floorplan includes kitchen island/breakfast bar, pantry, SS appliances including gas range, granite countertops. 4th Bedroom is also perfect for home office, workout room or game room.  Large primary retreat with spa like bath, separate tub and shower, double sinks and walk in closet.  All appliances are included, water softner and 3 car garage, too!!
